<div><head>《文釋》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-1a.2">離黃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-1a.3">倉庚也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-1a.4">鳴則蠶生。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-1a.5">陸德明《爾雅‧釋文》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-1a.6">揣摩揣人主之情，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-1a.7">摩而近之也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-1a.8">《史記‧蘇秦列傳》司馬貞《索隱》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-2a.2">瓠巴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-2a.3">齊人也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-2a.4">《文選‧馬季長長笛賦》李善注。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-2a.5">《管子》曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-2a.6">夫士懷耿介之心，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-2a.7">不蔭惡木之枝，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-2a.8">惡木尚能恥之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-2a.9">況與惡人同處！<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-2a.10">《文選‧陸士衡猛虎行》注引李善曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-2a.11">今撿《管子》，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-2a.12">近亡數篇，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-2a.13">恐是亡篇之內，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1484_CHANT_001-2a.14">而邃見之。<lb/></seg>
</p>
